# Spending & Approval Thresholds

## Spending
| Threshold | Rule |
|---|---|
| Under {{spendingLimit}} | Can be delegated/spent without approval |
| {{spendingLimit}}+ | Needs {{userName}}'s approval |

## Requires approval
- Live financial transactions
- Contract signing
- First-time purchase categories (then autonomous for that type)

## Hard delegation boundaries
NEVER delegate emotional or relational matters. These require the human's personal touch.
